The intent is for the `context.qb` format to become a community-maintained
standard. The CC-BY-4.0 license allows anyone to use, fork, and extend the
format while preserving attribution to the ContextQB project.

Tooling code (the CLI, validator, etc.) is MIT-licensed; see the parent
directory's LICENSE file.
